data.title: 以 1 到 3 分钟谈论以下主题
data.content: Describe a memory of your favorite vacation or trip. How old were you, and who was with you? What is the happiest part of this memory?
data.answer: When I was eight years old and my family took our first big vacation to Florida to go to Disney World. This was my favorite vocation because it was the first time my family had ever been anywhere far away together. I was overwhelmed with all the shops, vendors, and especially the castle! My favorite part was that I can actually meet the characters, Goofy was my favorite! I’ll never forget that vacation and I can’t wait to make new vacation memories!（86 字）
